CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF THE FOLLOWING: SUGAR, NONFAT DRY MILK, YEAST, DOUGH CONDITIONERS (MONOGLYCERIDES, SODIUM STEAROYL LACTYLATE, DEODORIZED GARLIC, ASCORBIC ACID), SALT, SPICES.
